text: Kincaid Lake State Park is a park located near Falmouth, Kentucky in Pendleton County. The park encompasses . Recreational activities include boating, fishing, miniature golf, hiking, and swimming. ==References== ==External links== *Kincaid Lake State Parks Kentucky State Parks Category:State parks of Kentucky Category:Protected areas of Pendleton County, Kentucky Category:Protected areas established in 1963
